                <p>The Global NCAP rating process rigorously tests vehicles for adult and child occupant protection during frontal, side, and pedestrian crashes. The Tata Curvv excelled in all parameters, thanks to its reinforced structure and advanced safety technologies like multiple airbags, ABS with EBD, electronic stability control, and a high-strength body shell.</p>
